Like we're just
supposed to accept it.

40:57.989 --> 40:59.923
I<i> don't</i> accept that.

40:59.925 --> 41:02.258
So, what are you gonna do?

41:02.260 --> 41:03.460
I don't know.

41:04.796 --> 41:06.629
But I'm gonna do
<i> something.</i>

41:06.631 --> 41:08.631
[ ringing ]
[ sighs ]

41:08.633 --> 41:10.433
<i> You've reached avery.</i>
