41:10.435 --> 41:12.068
[<i> beep</i> ]
[ voice breaking ]
hey, it's me.

41:12.070 --> 41:14.571
Um, I'm guessing
that you've heard

41:14.573 --> 41:17.140
That autumn went with the exes.

41:17.142 --> 41:19.776
Glenn says that I-I shouldn't
worry about it,

41:19.778 --> 41:21.377
That everything's
gonna be okay, but...

41:24.449 --> 41:27.750
Anyway, you said I could call,
so I'm calling.

41:27.752 --> 41:28.818
But you're not there.

41:28.820 --> 41:30.587
[ chuckles ]

41:30.589 --> 41:31.988
So...

41:33.658 --> 41:36.192
[ sobbing ]

41:37.429 --> 41:38.428
Hey.

41:38.430 --> 41:40.797
Hey.

41:40.799 --> 41:43.099
I, uh, heard on the news
you pulled out of the movie.

41:43.101 --> 41:45.301
I did.

41:45.303 --> 41:50.773
Well, since you're
gonna be around more...

41:50.775 --> 41:53.309
Maybe you should have more time
with cadence after all.

41:53.311 --> 41:55.178
[ exhales sharply ]

41:55.180 --> 41:57.180
Hi.

41:57.182 --> 41:59.182
Hi, baby.

41:59.184 --> 42:00.850
I'll come get her
in two hours?

42:00.852 --> 42:02.418
Okay.

42:02.420 --> 42:03.686
Okay.

42:04.823 --> 42:06.990
Hey, avery.

42:06.992 --> 42:09.859
I didn't drop out of the movie
so you'd change your mind.

42:11.196 --> 42:12.862
I didn't change my mind

42:12.864 --> 42:14.063
Because you dropped out
of the movie.
